title: Jimmy Pardo
description: Jimmy Pardo (Never Not Funny! Conan! Comedy!) is such a delightful YMIW guest: funny, thoughtful, just a deep AND riffing machine. The Sleepy Summer Series continues with NO A/C but still A DELIGHT! So glad the Podfather came by! Get into it, you weirdos!!
